### Local Testing for GitHub Copilot SDK Azure Functions
### Run with: func start
### Base URL: http://localhost:7071

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071

### ============================================
### ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Auth Status - Check if GITHUB_TOKEN is configured
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/auth-status

### Chat - Basic prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What tools do you have?"
}

### Chat - Code question
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What are the different agent types in Foundry?"
}

### Chat - With custom timeout
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Explain the difference between async and sync programming",
    "timeout": 60
}
